<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Affiliate</strong></h3>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="privacy-policy-box" width="3/4"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1484127217662{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"]means a legal entity that controls, is controlled by or is under common control with another legal entity, but only while that control relationship exists. To "control" means the direct or indirect ownership or power to control of more than 50% of the issued shares or other securities of an entity or of the voting rights attached to the issued shares or other securities of such entity; or the power to control, directly or indirectly, the appointment of more than 50% of any board of directors or governing body of such entity.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner el_class="privacy-policy-box" width="1/4"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1484127371072{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"]
